            <title><![CDATA[Elden Ring Nightreign shipments and digital sales top five million; Elden Ring expansion ‘Shadow of the Erdtree’ tops 10 million]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gematsu.com/2025/07/elden-ring-nightreign-shipments-and-digital-sales-top-five-million-elden-ring-expansion-shadow-of-the-erdtree-tops-10-million</link>
            <guid>https://www.resetera.com/threads/elden-ring-nightreign-shipments-and-digital-sales-top-five-million-elden-ring-expansion-%E2%80%98shadow-of-the-erdtree%E2%80%99-tops-10-million.1252197/</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div>

    <ul>
    <li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps4">PS4</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PS5</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-one">Xbox One</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a></li>    </ul>

    
    <p><span>New sales milestone achieved.</span>
      </p></div><div><p>Total worldwide shipments and digital sales for <em><a title="Games > Elden Ring Nightreign [9 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/elden-ring-nightreign">Elden Ring Nightreign</a></em> have surpassed five million units, and <em><a title="Games > Elden Ring [33 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/elden-ring">Elden Ring</a></em> expansion “Shadow of the Erdtree” has surpassed 10 million units, publisher <a title="Companies > Bandai Namco Entertainment [6,723 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/bandai-namco-entertainment">Bandai Namco</a> and developer <a title="Companies > FromSoftware [401 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/kadokawa-corporation/fromsoftware">FromSoftware</a> <a href="https://www.fromsoftware.jp/ww/pressrelease_detail.html?tgt=20250724_eldenring_nightreign_salesdata" target="_blank">announced</a>. <span id="more-979975"></span></p><p><em>Elden Ring Nightreign</em> launched for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [9,952 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > Xbox Series [7,567 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a>, <a title="Platforms > PS4 [28,183 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps4">PlayStation 4</a>, <a title="Platforms > Xbox One [14,082 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-one">Xbox One</a>, and <a title="Platforms > PC [23,726 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2622380/ELDEN_RING_NIGHTREIGN/" target="_blank">Steam</a> today on May 30, and surpassed <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2025/05/elden-ring-nightreign-shipments-and-digital-sales-top-two-million-in-one-day">two million</a> shipments and digital sales in one day. It was <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2025/06/elden-ring-nightreign-shipments-and-digital-sales-top-3-5-million">last reported</a> to have surpassed 3.5 million units on June 3.</p><p><em>Elden Ring</em> expansion “Shadow of the Erdtree” launched on February 25, 2022, and was <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2024/06/elden-ring-expansion-shadow-of-the-erdtree-sales-top-five-million-in-three-days">last reported</a> to have shipped five million units within its first three days of release. <em>Elden Ring</em>, which is required to play the expansion, is available for PlayStation 5, Xbox Series, PlayStation 4, Xbox One, and PC via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1245620/ELDEN_RING/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a>. A Switch 2 version is <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2025/04/elden-ring-tarnished-edition-announced-for-switch-2">due out in 2025</a>.</p></div></div><br/><br/>https://www.gematsu.com/2025/07/elden-ring-nightreign-shipments-and-digital-sales-top-five-million-elden-ring-expansion-shadow-of-the-erdtree-tops-10-million]]></content:encoded>
